       "top.gif"></a></font></font></p>

  <p>Registration can be done online at <font color=
  "#0000FF"><u><a href=
  "http://www.LifeCoachTraining.com/">www.LifeCoachTraining.com</a></u></font>
  or by calling Edwina Adams at (972) 867-1915. We accept Visa,
  MasterCard, American Express, check, or money order. Payment
  plans are available.</p>

  <p>If you have further questions regarding the Christian Track,
  please contact Christopher McCluskey at <font color=
  "#0000FF"><u><a href=
  "http://www.christian-living.com/">chris@christian-living.com</a></u></font>
  or Judy Santos at <font color="#0000FF"><u><a href=
  "mailto:coach@judysantos.com">coach@judysantos.com</a></u></font>.</p>

  <p>Three articles on transitioning into life coaching are
  available upon request at <font color="#0000FF"><u><a href=
  "http://www.christian-living.com/">www.christian-living.com</a></u></font>.
  You can also download two chapters from the book <i>Christian
  Coaching</i> on that site, which will give you a sense of
  coaching in practice.</p>

  <p>To get a sense of what other Christians are doing in the field
  of life coaching, visit the Christian Coaches Network at
  <font color="#0000FF"><u><a href=
  "http://www.christiancoaches.com/">www.christiancoaches.com</a></u></font>.</p><br>

